1. For any sorted array , try to approach binary search
2. if there is increasing section as well as decreasing section in array, try to solve by bynary search
3. if logn is expected definitely its a binary search questions
4. if nlogn is asked definitely the question has something to do with binary search and
iterating an array for at least one time.
5. if target is not given and you are asked to perform any action then you must
do while (start<end) and not while ( start <=end).
6.Whenever asked minimize the greatest distance or minimize the greatest something, do binary search as done in allocation
of books question.